    theta = np.pi / 6
    rotation_x = np.array([[1, 0, 0, 0],[0, np.cos(theta), -np.sin(theta), 0],[0, np.sin(theta), np.cos(theta), 0], [0, 0, 0, 1]])
    mesh.apply_transform(rotation_x)
